Package: crontabR
Type: Package
Title: Easy Script Scheduling in R for Linux
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Eric Bailey
Maintainer: Eric Bailey <eb11307@gmail.com>
Description:
  Provides an interface to your personal crontab in R. Set R scripts to run at
  specific intervals. Use the RStudio addin for an easy graphical way to schedule
  tasks in R under a Linux environment.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
Depends:
  shiny,
  miniUI,
  DT,
  lubridate
